title: Patty Duke Films - 68 complete, 3 partial out of 119 lifetime
description:
Included here are all the acting performance videos of Patty Duke in movies, film shorts, and one-time TV films that I could find. The TV videos include TV movies, the old-time live theatre plays, mini-series, and anthology TV series where every episode had a unique story and different actors. Not included are regular TV series where the main characters return on each episode.
